    "Rows with missing `user_answer` values are removed because unanswered questions\n",

   "source": [
    "## 8. Remove Duplicate Records\n",
    "\n",
    "Duplicate rows are removed based on user ID, question ID, and timestamp."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 56,
   "id": "e4a189bb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "np.int64(2)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 56,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "df.duplicated(\n",
    "    subset=[\"user_id\", \"question_id\", \"timestamp\"]\n",
    ").sum()\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 57,
   "id": "e013a700",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df = df.drop_duplicates(\n",
    "    subset=[\"user_id\", \"question_id\", \"timestamp\"]\n",
    ")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "43aaae25",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 9. Standardize User Answers\n",
    "\n",
    "User answers are standardized to lowercase and stripped of whitespace\n",
    "to ensure consistent categorical values.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 58,
   "id": "e094856a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df[\"user_answer\"] = (\n",
    "    df[\"user_answer\"]\n",
    "    .str.lower()\n",
    "    .str.strip()\n",
    ")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3c898fbd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 10. Validate Identifiers\n",
    "\n",
    "We validate key identifiers to ensure correct formatting and data integrity.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 59,
   "id": "92b99fde",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# question_id format\n",
    "df = df[df[\"question_id\"].str.match(r\"^q\\d+$\")]\n",
    "\n",
    "# user_id validity\n",
    "df = df[df[\"user_id\"].notna() & (df[\"user_id\"].str.strip() != \"\")]\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a9fc481c",
